title: Unstuffed Cabbage
directions: In a large skillet, heat olive oil over medium heat. Add the ground beef and onion and cook, stirring, until ground beef is no longer pink and onion is tender.
Add the chopped cabbage, tomatoes, pepper, and salt. Bring to a boil. Cover and simmer for 20 to 30 minutes, or until cabbage is tender.
ingredients: 2 cans (28 ounces each) petite diced tomatoes
